description: AMUNDI PRIME UK MID AND SMALL CAP - UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, the performance of the Solactive United Kingdom Mid & Small Cap ex Investment Trust Index (Net Total return) whether it is rising or falling. This ETF offers exposure to mid and small-cap companies on the UK market. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus or www.solactive.com.
name: Amundi Prime UK Mid & Small Cap UCITS ETF DR - GBP (D)
